      "writtenOn": "2018-01-04T03:06:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "ah, true :( And we don\u0027t want to import protos into common/api/gitiles package.\nI\u0027d personally name proto/gitiles as \"proto/gitilespb\", so my editor does more work for me, but then we have inconsistent naming inside common/proto/*, unless we append \"pb\" to all of them (WDYT about that?).\n\nthis discussion shouldn\u0027t block this CL landing though.",
      "parentUuid": "9f150f86_38a60471",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 29,
        "startChar": 1,
