      "message": "pb suffix in package names is not what everyone else are doing :(\n\nhttps://godoc.org/github.com/golang/protobuf/ptypes#pkg-subdirectories\nhttps://godoc.org/?q\u003dproto\n\nwe might want to use type aliases in go1.9 to make gitiltespb types available in gitiles package.",
      "parentUuid": "bd640ee1_14f57df8",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 29,
        "startChar": 1,
